import React, {useState} from 'react'
import { Form } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const AddWorld = () => (
  <Form className = "add-world">
    <Form.Group widths='equal'>
      <Form.Field label='Name of the world' control='input' />
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group grouped>
      <label>Type of World</label>
      <Form.Field
        label='Public'
        control='input'
        type='radio'
        name='htmlRadios'
      />
      <Form.Field
        label='Private'
        control='input'
        type='radio'
        name='htmlRadios'
      />
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group grouped>
      <label>Join with Moderator Approval?</label>
      <Form.Field
        label='Yes'
        control='input'
        type='radio'
        name='htmlRadios2'
      />
      <Form.Field
        label='No'
        control='input'
        type='radio'
        name='htmlRadios2'
      />
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Field label='Description of the World' control='textarea' rows='3' />
    <Form.Field control='button'>
      Create World
    </Form.Field>
  </Form>
)

export default AddWorld;
